<item>
            <title>[LU-6605] redhat 4</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6605</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I want to mount lustre in Red Hat 4 system. I cannot find support software on the public website. I type mount.lustre, and the error message shows &quot;command not found&quot;. What&apos;s the problem?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
